race.comment: The well-related NOW IS THE HOUR (6) (full to 2xG3 winner and G2 placed Inkaruna) is a consistent commodity who is yet to miss the top-five in nine career starts. Boasts a win and a placing from two attempts over this track and trip and is racing in a rich vein of form since joining the Gollan yard. Rates the testing material. ALTERMATUM (10) loves this six-furlong journey with two wins and two seconds from just five starts. Brings Victorian formlines to the table and any market support must be noted. VOODOO LASS (11) resumes here but put a hat-trick of wins together before the spell and has had two trials in preparation for this. Can run a big race while fresh. SOUTHERN CHARM (4) has gotten better with each run this time in and will be cherry-ripe now fourth-up. In the mix. THAT'S INTERESTING (15) next in line with the claim from the inside marble.
